# Base URL of the backend API server.
# Set this for production / static deployments (e.g. GitHub Pages, Vercel, etc.)
# where the backend is NOT on the same hostname:3100 as the frontend.
# If unset, the app falls back to <current-origin>:3100 (suitable for local/LAN dev).
#
# Local dev uses 127.0.0.1 (not localhost) on purpose: when another project holds
# the port via IPv6 (::1), `localhost` can resolve to ::1 and hit the wrong server
# during SSR (node fetch). 127.0.0.1 pins it to this project's backend (port 3100).
# Frontend dev runs on port 4173 (strictPort) — see vite.config.ts.
# Example (production): PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3100

# Google Analytics 4 측정 ID (예: G-XXXXXXXXXX). 미설정 시 분석 비활성.
# PUBLIC_GA_ID=

# Google AdSense 퍼블리셔 ID는 src/app.html <head>에 직접 박혀 있다(SPA 사이트 확인 안정성).
# 광고 슬롯은 src/app/view/ad/AdUnit.svelte 의 client 상수와 함께 관리.
